<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /></head><body><table cellspacing="0" border="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin-left:0pt;mso-padding-alt:0.7500000000000001pt 0.7500000000000001pt 0.7500000000000001pt 0.7500000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;mso-border-insidev:none;mso-border-insideh:none;"><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">У меня потрясающая новость! Мне предложили работу в Японии! </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Василий </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Ты серьёзно? Какая удача! Но ты же не говоришь по-японски. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Контракт начинается через полгода, за это время я должен заговорить по-японски... </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Василий </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Это же такой сложный язык! Что ты собираешься делать? </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Я уже купил самоучитель по японскому и позвонил в лучшую языковую школу города, буду ходить на языковые курсы два раза в неделю. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Василий </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">А может лучше заниматься с репетитором? Частные уроки очень помогают, в языковой школе ты будешь работать в группе. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">В нашем городе так трудно найти репетитора! А в языковом центре я буду читать по-японски, смотреть фильмы в оригинале, учить диалоги, писать диктанты, аудирования. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Василий </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">За полгода трудно будет преодолеть языковой барьер... а преподаватель в этой школе-носитель языка? </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Да, и мне это нравится. А вообще я не очень волнуюсь, думаю, что самый лучший способ учить язык- это поехать в страну, где на нём говорят. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Василий </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Да, или найти себе иностранных друзей. </span></p></td></tr><tr><td width="78" style="width:58.80666861466537pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000"><b>Иван </b></span></p></td><td width="116" style="width:86.62647360974411pt;padding:6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt 6.000000000000001pt;border-left:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-top:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-right:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;border-bottom:0.7499999999999999pt solid #000000;"><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;mso-border-left-alt:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;mso-border-right-alt:none;mso-border-bottom-alt:none;mso-border-between:none"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman';font-size:12pt;color:#000000;mso-style-textfill-fill-color:#000000">Мне не терпится начать учить этот язык! </span></p></td></tr></table><p style="margin-top:0pt;margin-bottom:0pt;border:none;border-left:none;border-top:none;border-right:none;border-bottom:none;mso-border-between:none">&nbsp;</p></body></html>